" for the main land cover transitions (by area) should be reported in "
"tables SO1-2.T3 and SO1-2.T4 for the baseline and reporting periods, "
"respectively. Land productivity degradation (i.e. derived from the three-"
"class in the last column of table 13) in the reporting period should be "
