#: ../../SO1.md:901
msgid "Step 7:  Verify the results"
msgstr "第7步：验证结果"

#: ../../SO1.md:903
msgid ""
"The seasonal dynamics of productivity vary greatly across the globe, "
"strongly influenced by the prevailing climatic conditions and land "
"management practices. This may affect the reliability of applying "
"estimates of land productivity from global data sources to local areas "
"and require inputs from national experts to detect and highlight "
"situations where the confidence level of the obtained results might be "
"low. This input would contribute to a qualitative assessment of the "
"reliability of the estimates."
msgstr "生产力的季节性动态在全球范围内差异很大，受到普遍的气候条件和土地管理方法的极大影响。这可能会影响到将全球数据来源的土地生产力估计值应用于局部地区的可靠性，需要国家专家的投入才能发现和强调所获结果的置信度可能较低的情况。这种投入将有助于对估计数的可靠性进行定性评估。"

#: ../../SO1.md:905
msgid "Step 8: Generate reports"
msgstr "第8步：生成报告"

#: ../../SO1.md:907
msgid ""
"Once verified by the Parties, the estimates of land productivity dynamics"
" and land degradation for the reporting and baseline periods should be "
"officially submitted to UNCCD. Parties are also encouraged to submit "
"narratives on the methodology, data sources and data accuracy in case the"
" estimates are derived from national data. It would also be beneficial to"
" report on special cases and issues, describing any deviation from the "
"default method and providing the rationale to adopt a different "
"methodology. A general comment field is provided at the end of the "
"reporting form in the PRAIS 4 platform for this purpose."
msgstr ""
"经缔约方核实后，报告期和基线期的土地生产力动态和土地退化估计数应正式提交给《荒漠化公约》。还鼓励缔约方提交关于方法、数据来源和数据准确性的说明（如果估计数是来自国家数据的话）。报告特殊情况和问题也是有益的，从而可以说明任何偏离默认方法的情况并提供采用不同方法的理由。为此，PRAIS"
" 4平台的报告表单末尾提供了一个“一般性注释”栏。"

#: ../../SO1.md:909
msgid ""
"Information on land productivity dynamics and land productivity "
"degradation should be reported in km2 for the entire country."
msgstr "关于整个国家土地生产力动态和土地生产力退化的信息应以平方公里为单位进行报告。"

#: ../../SO1.md:911
msgid ""
"If the default datasets are replaced with national land cover data, "
"countries are encouraged to make the relevant geospatial data and "
"relevant metadata available in the PRAIS 4 platform."
msgstr "如果默认数据集被国家土地覆盖数据取代，鼓励各国在PRAIS 4平台上提供相关地理空间数据和相关元数据。"

